#!new # vim:syntax=sh:tw=72

# REQUIREMENTS & DEFAULTS
#-require SRCS=[a-zA-Z].*[.]c.*
--default APPS=/apps
--default VERS=0.0

# BRIEF
#! Creates CmakeLists.txt for named PROJECT that uses cmake

=pod

=head1 NAME

B<cpp-cmake template> - Creates a simple cmake project for C/C++

=head1 SYNOPSIS

B<new> cpp-cmake I<OPTIONS> {:I<NAME>:} SRCS="I<LIST_OF_FILES> VERS=N.M"

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Creates a basic CMakeLists.txt file needed to build C/C++ projects.

=head1 PARAMETERS

=over

=item SRCS

List of plain file names for source files.

=item VERS

Version number #.# (defaults to 0.0)

=back

=head1 REQUIREMENTS

An appropriate version of cmake version 3.11 or better should be installed.

